name: The Best BBQ Sauce Recipe - @FoodNFTs
description: I'm a semi-professional chef and foodie. This is the PERFECT barbecue sauce recipe for beef, pork or chicken. Here's the recipe: 2 cups ketchup 1/4 cup molasses 3 tsp Worcestershire sauce 2 tbsp lemon juice 1/2 medium onion 1/4 cup of unsalted butter 1/2 tsp tabasco sauce 3/8 cups dark brown sugar 1/2 tsp cayenne pepper 2 cloves garlic 1 tbsp black pepper
